title.narrative: Procurement of Goods for Maternal and Newborn Child Health Programme

description.narrative: This activity (Procurement of Goods for Maternal and Newborn Child Health Programme) is a component of Maternal and Newborn Child Health Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of goods' and a budget of £28,845,553. This component benefits Nigeria, and works in the following sector(s): Basic health care, Reproductive health care, Family planning. , with the following implementing partners: AECOM, Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 01-04-2014 and the end date is 30-04-2020.
